Method Detail

createUser

java.lang.Object createUser()
This API creates a User, signin the user and returns JSESSIONID. The User can be either a Passenger or a Driver. It does not require the user to be signed in.
Parameters:
url - /user/createUser
input-sample-1 - {"tenantname":"WorldTaxi","firstName":"David","lastName":"Ultrafast","username":"dultrafast","password":"Welcome!1","phone":"773-329-1784","email":"dultrafast@worldtaxi.com","locale":"en-US","driver":{"carType":"SEDAN","servedLocation":"Chicago, IL, USA","radiusServed":"RADIUS_50","activeStatus":"ENABLED"}}
input-sample-2 - {"tenantname":"WorldTaxi","firstName":"John","lastName":"Airjunkie","username":"jairjunkie","password":"Welcome!1","phone":"773-329-1784","email":"jairjunkie@worldtaxi.com","locale":"en-US","passenger":{}}}
Returns:
output-sample {"type":"USER","code":"SUCCESS","message":"User dultrxafast created","JSESSIONID":"6317F9E37E0F499399A3F89DDA6D5723"}

retrieveAllUsers

@Secured(['ROLE_ADMIN','IS_AUTHENTICATED_FULLY'	])
java.lang.Object retrieveAllUsers()
This API retrieves all Users. This API is only available to users with the Administrator privilege.
Parameters:
url - /user/retrieveAllUsers
input-sample - {}
Returns:
output-sample {"users":[{"id":4,"version":1,"firstName":"Admin","lastName":"Admin","phone":"800-800-8080","email":"admin@worldtaxi.com"},{"id":5,"version":1,"firstName":"John","lastName":"Goodrider","phone":"800-800-8080","email":"jgoodrider@worldtaxi.com","passenger":{"id":5}},{"id":6,"version":1,"firstName":"John","lastName":"Goodarm","phone":"800-800-2020","email":"jgoodarm@worldtaxi.com","driver":{"id":6,"servedMetro":"Chicago-Naperville-Joliet, IL","carType":"VAN"}}]}

retrieveAllUsersAsJSONP

@Secured(['ROLE_ADMIN','IS_AUTHENTICATED_FULLY'	])
java.lang.Object retrieveAllUsersAsJSONP()
This API retrieves all Users. This API is only available to users with the Administrator privilege. The return users using the JSONP convention. Please use retrieveAllUsers instead.

retrieveLoggedUserDetails

@Secured(['ROLE_DRIVER','ROLE_PASSENGER','IS_AUTHENTICATED_FULLY'	])
java.lang.Object retrieveLoggedUserDetails()
This API retrieves the details of the user currently logged in. It is useful to obtain the id of the user for use in subsequent calls.
Parameters:
url - /user/retrieveLoggedUserDetails
input-sample - {}
Returns:
output-sample {"user":{"id":5,"version":1,"firstName":"John","lastName":"Goodrider","phone":"800-800-8080","email":"jgoodrider@worldtaxi.com","passenger":{"id":5}}}

retrieveUserDetailById

@Secured(['ROLE_ADMIN','IS_AUTHENTICATED_FULLY'	])
java.lang.Object retrieveUserDetailById()
This API is retrieves a User by id. This API is only available to users with the Administrator privilege.
Parameters:
url - /user/retrieveUserDetailById
input-sample - {"id":"6"}
Returns:
output-sample {"user":{"id":6,"version":1,"firstName":"John","lastName":"Goodarm","phone":"800-800-2020","email":"jgoodarm@worldtaxi.com","driver":{"id":6,"servedMetro":"Chicago-Naperville-Joliet, IL","carType":"VAN"}}}
